''Dental pharmacology''' is the study of drugs used to treat conditions of the [[oral cavity]].{{citation needed|date=July 2017}}

Some of these drugs include [[antibiotics]], [[analgesic]]s, [[Anti-inflammatory|anti-inflammatory drugs]] and anti-[[periodontitis]] agents.{{citation needed|date=July 2017}}

